### Enrichment
Markdown Fixup (Jan 2026) is an opinionated linter that works in pipelines following Unix philosophy. Flowmark is a modern formatter with semantic line breaks and LLM pipeline support. PyMarkdown uses structure-aware token analysis. markdownlint-cli2 v0.22.0 enables CI/CD style guide enforcement. The SourceNormalizer plugin pattern aligns with these tools. Consider benchmarking against existing linters.

